---
import Link from "./Link.astro";
import ProjectHeader from "./ProjectHeader.astro";
import SmallHeading from "./SmallHeading.astro";

import SectionHeader from "./SectionHeader.astro";

let types = ["Electronic", "Ambient", "Experimental", "Folk", "Pop"];
---

<div
  class="load-in flex flex-col lg:grid grid-cols-2 text-lg lg:divide-x border-b"
>
  <div class="col-span-1 p-4 sm:p-8 sm:pb-16">
    <SmallHeading text="Winter Foe" />
    Winter Foe is a music project that I have been working on since around 2018.
    I am searching for new ways to combine digital sounds, electronics, acoustic
    instruments, and field recordings. Through this project I have expanded my
    visual vocabulary by producing album art, animations, and videos. I have
    also had the opportunity to collaborate with some amazing musicians.

    <div
      class="flex-col sm:flex-row flex flex-wrap gap-4 sm:gap-12 my-4 sm:mb-0 sm:mt-8"
    >
      <Link
        href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/4GYawQUhnxYepBC7WhUJ4N"
        name="Spotify"
      />
      <Link
        href="https://music.apple.com/us/artist/winter-foe/1336473956"
        name="Apple Music"
      />
      <Link href="https://winterfoe.bandcamp.com/" name="Bandcamp" />
      <Link href="https://soundcloud.com/winter-foe" name="Soundcloud" />
    </div>
    <slot />
  </div>
  <div
    class="hidden sm:flex justify-between gap-12 col-span-1 p-4 sm:p-8 sm:pb-16"
  >
    <div>
      <div class="mb-4">
        <SmallHeading text="Genres" />
      </div>
      <div class={types.length > 0 ? "hidden sm:block" : "hidden"}>
        {types.map((type) => <p class="">{type}</p>)}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <SmallHeading text="Year" />
      </div>
      <p class="">2018 â€“ Present</p>
    </div>
    <div class="invisible">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <SmallHeading text="Collaborators" />
      </div>
      <div>Collaborators</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="load-in flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-stretch">
  <div class="md:flex-1">
    <iframe
      width="100%"
      height="750"
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ci7wcKekVwo?si=Cjjt6Is0VnBBdF_y"
      title="YouTube video player"
      frameborder="0"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
      allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  #manipulate {
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }
</style>
